      FROM moz_places
      WHERE

          hash('http://www.' || :strippedURL)
        )
        AND frecency <> 0
      ORDER BY

        title || '/' <> :strippedURL DESC,
        url = :inputedURL DESC,
        frecency DESC,
        id DESC
      LIMIT 1
